rows.label: qst200710_msg0001
rows.name:
You guys?! What are
you doing here-mau?!

rows.label: qst200710_msg0002
rows.name:
You're the one who told us to steal
the emperor's underwear, right?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0003
rows.name: What is Maumau doing here, mo?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0004
rows.name: Maumau was about to sneak in-mau.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0005
rows.name:
You guys can stay here and get
held up by the guards-mau!

rows.label: qst200710_msg0006
rows.name:
...Hmm, it certainly looks
difficult to persuade that guard.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0007
rows.name:
Could Idaten get it
without being seen, mo?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0008
rows.name: Should we have Idaten get it?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0018
rows.name:
That's a bit difficult-ppo!
At my current speed, the
guards will catch me-ppo!

rows.label: qst200710_msg0012
rows.name:
Well, even if Idaten can't
go, with Meleph here, we
can get in without issue.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0014
rows.name:
...I can get us in, but I'm
not particularly keen on it.

rows.label: qst200710_msg0015
rows.name:
In the first place, for me, his older
sister, to go and get my brother's
underwear... is that not a strange story...?

rows.label: qst200710_msg0016
rows.name:
Now, now, don't say that.
It's for Idaten's sake.
